General Guidelines For Charts\
-Label Axes\
-Make Font Readable for value labels\
-Space increments out so there is not too many or too little (about 10)\
-Box the entire area for data\
-Use gridlines\
-Provide a legend if / when needed (ideally in the chart box)\
-Or label items directly\
\
