-Colors in Moderation - Equal amount of gray scale and color\
-No Super bright Colors\
-Opacity of 75% (To see gridlines)\
-Consider the meaning of color (Red bad, Green Money)\
-Consider 1 primary color and 1 secondary color\
-Use color to highlight a specific point\
